.\" Manpage for rclonefzf
.TH rclonefzf 1 "2026-01-06" "2.0.1" "rclonefzf manual"

.SH NAME
rclonefzf \- interactively search, install, and remove AUR packages using fzf


.SH SYNOPSIS
.B rclonefzf [\fIOPTIONS\fR] [\fISEARCH QUERY\fR]


.SH DESCRIPTION
Search, install, and remove packages from the AUR interactively with fzf.


.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-h
Show the help menu

.TP
.B \-\-help
Show the extended help menu

.TP
.B \-k, \-\-keybindings
List keybindings for rclonefzf

.TP
.B \-V, \-\-version
Show version of rclonefzf

.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
.B $ rclonefzf
Run rclonefzf with no search query

.TP
.B $ rclonefzf fzf
Search for 'fzf' with rclonefzf

.TP
.B $ rclonefzf \-h
Show the help menu


